PRE-REQUISITES
********************************************

1) add / remove keywwords under column E "Log keyword" which you want in our report

2)  Copy all long run logs inside folder "Logs_long_run"

3) Update line number 35 of python code with path  "/home/sim/Documents/SHM/Testing/Log_Automation_Report/Log_Automation/Logs_long_run"

4) execute linux cmd "pip install xlrd"

5)  execute linux cmd "pip install xlwt"

6)  execute  cmd on ubuntu   "python Integrated_Log_Automation.py"

7)  In case of windows set environment variable & install all python dependencies  "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mXXlt9bFIuI" . But recommend to use on ubuntu.


